  "detailed_description": "Voxel Printer is the voxel art crafting game similar to Minecraft that up to 12 players compete with building cubes.<br><br>Create a your work that fits topic within the time given.<br>There is a voting for the best work after the round is over.<br>The work with the most votes wins the game.<br><br>You can also extract your work as an FBX file.<br>And please use your masterpiece in several places.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1100860/extras/167297c7534cd0ac01014653d4ea46b6.poster.avif?t=1660566687\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1100860/extras/167297c7534cd0ac01014653d4ea46b6.webm?t=1660566687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1100860/extras/167297c7534cd0ac01014653d4ea46b6.mp4?t=1660566687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1100860/extras/f90f9e02465895f8a62689192e0692c7.poster.avif?t=1660566687\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1100860/extras/f90f9e02465895f8a62689192e0692c7.webm?t=1660566687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1100860/extras/f90f9e02465895f8a62689192e0692c7.mp4?t=1660566687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1100860/extras/e2f681c11f8b1ae595105e83a9a476ea.poster.avif?t=1660566687\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto